      <div class="cta-block">
        <h2>Free Palmerston inspection quote.</h2>
        <p>House, townhouse, body-corporate or pre-purchase. Same-day inspections most weeks.</p>
        <div class="hero-actions" style="justify-content:center;">
          <a class="btn btn-primary" href="tel:+61390030108">&#9742; Call (03) 9003 0108</a>
